data.title: Patric Skog - Woodblock Studio - Session Guitarist / Producer - Stockholm
data.meta_description: Session Guitarist / Producer Patric Skog - Woodblock Studio - Listen to samples, read reviews, learn more, contact. Read interview with Patric Skog - Woodbl...
data.text:
Hello! My name is Patric and I am a professional guitarist from Stockholm, Sweden. I would love to record any electric or acoustic guitar tracks for your songs.

I provide clients around the world with high quality acoustic and electric guitar tracks from my professional studio in Stockholm, Sweden. All I need is an mp3 or wav of your song with any instruction and I will deliver tracks to you within a few short days! I also play mandolin, Lap steel and electric bass.

There's nothing I enjoy more than communicating with artists and songwriters, taking the music to the next level. I use my collection of vintage guitars, amps, but also modern gear and my favorite plug-ins. My goal is to make your track as great as it can be!

I have extensive experience from 20 years of live and studio work, a large number of tracks recorded for various artists in the "Eurovision Song Contest", experience in film scoring (composing and recording),also a Berklee alumni.

I'd love to hear about your project. Click the 'Contact' button above to get in touch.

Tell me about your project and how I can help, through the 'Contact' button above.
